I wrote like this by using union type `string | Buffer`. However, the original author may prefer to define separately like the following.

```ts
load(html: string, options?: CheerioOptionsInterface): CheerioStatic;
load(html: Buffer, options?: CheerioOptionsInterface): CheerioStatic;
```

I'd like to change the definition when you suggest.

